00:45:24,697 --> 00:45:27,237
<i>Nepovedala ti niečo?</i>

495
00:45:27,237 --> 00:45:30,264
Nie, nič mi nepovedala.

496
00:45:30,264 --> 00:45:34,487
Mrzí ma to, 
