497
00:45:34,487 --> 00:45:36,755
<i>Znie to, akoby sa niečo dialo.</i>

498
00:45:39,353 --> 00:45:41,875
Súvisí to s jej náčrtmi?

499
00:45:43,534 --> 00:45:46,574
Ak seržantka Yoo nechcela 
o tom hovoriť,

500
00:45:46,574 --> 00:45:49,679
